## ⚠️ Risks & Critical Checks

🔴 CRITICAL: Text becomes unreadable in Day or Night mode (contrast issues)  
🔴 CRITICAL: Theme setting does not persist as per product expectations  
🟡 Risk: Inconsistent theme between pages or browsers  
🟢 Desirable: Smooth theme switch with no layout jumps or performance issues

---

## ✅ Expected Behavior

✅ Users can easily toggle between Day and Night modes from the main Askeal UI.  
✅ The entire interface (chat, lists, footer, dialogs) follows the selected theme with good readability.  
✅ The chosen theme persists appropriately after refresh and navigation, and behavior is consistent across supported browsers.

